      Product Description

      Manufacturer, Wholesaler & Retailer of finest quality beddings from Jaipur. Our products are extremely design centric, created out of the highest quality materials. Each of our product is made only from high quality cotton fabric to make sure the fabric is soft, skin-friendly and long lasting. We make our products in both Traditional Hand Block Print & Hand Screen Print and Machine Screen Print. All the images of our products are original with minimum edits for superior customer experience.

      Premium Cotton Blend

      All our products are made from Premium Cotton sourced all over from India.

      Pre Shrunk Fabric

      All our products comes with pre shrunk fabric which makes sure that the fabric does not shrink even after multiple washes.

      Fast Colors

      All the colors while manufacturing your product are hand picked to make sure that it lasts as much as it could.

      Proudly Made in Bharat

      From sourcing the fabric to printing, washing, finishing and supplying it to the end consumer, each and every process is done in India. We can say that all our products are proudly and purely Made in Bharat, India.

      Proudly Made in India

      All our products are Purely and Proudly Made in India with the help of traditional techniques which were taught by our ancestors. We are still following the old age techniques of Hand Screen Printing which gives employment to hundreds of employees and help them feed their families.

      Handcrafted in Rajasthan

      All our products are made in a small town of Jaipur called as 'Sanganer' which employees thousands of people.

      Each of your bed sheet goes through hundreds of hands in the process of Washing, Printing, Stitching & Finishing. Each process is traditional and most is done by human hands with minimum machine use.

      We are gratified in selling a product which is Proudly Made in India.

      Made from Traditional Techniques

      • Cotton Blend, Pre Shrunk Premium Fabric
      • Long Lasting Colors
      • Provides Employment to Hundreds of People, Directly & Indirectly.
      • Minimum Machinery used while making the whole product.
      • Care Instructions: Hand wash with cold water. Do not bleach, Dry in shade
      • Original Images with Minimum Edits

      About the Product

      • Premium Cotton Blend Fabric
      • Pre Shrunk Fabric
      • Double Bedsheet Size: 84 inch x 94 inch or 210 cms x 238 cms
      • Single Bedsheet Size: 58 inch x 84 inch or 147 cms 213 cms
      • Pillow Covers Size: 17.5 inch x 27.5 inch or 44 cm x 70 cm
      • Perfect gift for your loved ones
      • Proudly made in India from traditional techniques of Rajasthan
      • Care Instructions: Hand wash with cold water or machine wash with gentle cycle, Do not bleach, Dry in shade
